# PhishShield AI

PhishShield AI is a web-based phishing detection system that analyzes messages and identifies potential scam risks.

## Features
- Detects phishing messages
- Highlights suspicious keywords
- Identifies malicious links
- Provides AI-based explanation

## How it works
The system uses intelligent pattern detection to analyze text and classify it as safe or risky.

## Demo
Paste a suspicious message and click "Analyze" to see results.

